Hello, I’m Nazma from KU Game.
Nice to meet you! I’d like to learn more about your business model and main services.

Hi Nazma! Nice to meet you too. NewsBreak is the #1 most downloaded news app in the US, and our mission is to revitalize local news by connecting people with stories that matter in their communities. We offer native advertising through our Self-Serve Ad Platform, which allows advertisers like big brands, local businesses, e-commerce shops, and performance marketers to reach their ideal audience in a contextual environment. Our platform is AI-powered, constantly learning and optimizing to ensure your ads reach the right people at the right moment. We have 40M monthly active users and 16M daily active users who are engaged and have good purchasing power. If you're interested in driving sales, leads, app installs, or conversions, NewsBreak's platform can help you access this massive audience effectively. Let me know if you have any specific questions or need more details!
May I ask which countries you run promotions in?
NewsBreak is a US-only traffic source, so we run promotions exclusively within the United States. If you have any other questions or need further assistance, feel free to ask!
